2008-05-15  Roland Levillain  <roland@lrde.epita.fr>

	Pass option nostdinc to Automake.

	* configure.ac: Do it, to avoid inclusion problems in test
	directories hosting binaries with standard header names (e.g.,
	``set'' or ``list'').

